Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.36,0:21:57.55,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}終わらないメロディーを歌いだしました
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.54,0:22:05.74,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}とても大好きで　少し切なくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.98,0:22:07.38,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}でも　
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.62,0:22:13.40,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}止まることができなくて嫌いになりました
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.35,0:22:22.56,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}たとえ大切な君のそばでも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.92,0:22:27.39,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}life on the planet
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.86,0:22:33.07,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}見える景色は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.36,0:22:38.63,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}同じにはできないのです
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.85,0:22:50.26,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}心も　未来も　笑顔も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.47,0:22:57.17,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}そう　まだ見ぬ愛も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.36,0:23:01.03,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}Sweet love in love world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.28,0:23:05.05,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}Sweet love in love world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.25,0:23:08.64,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}You know what you wanna be
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.94,0:23:10.69,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}わかってんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.85,0:23:14.36,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}I can believe you tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.60,0:23:18.36,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}You see what I want tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.58,0:23:28.68,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}永遠と 儚さと 震える夜もあるけれど
