Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.36,0:21:57.55,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}吟唱出漫无止境的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.54,0:22:05.74,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}实在过于喜欢 同时伴随些许痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.98,0:22:07.38,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.62,0:22:13.40,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}由于无法停止已经开始厌倦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.35,0:22:22.56,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}即便在重要的你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.86,0:22:33.07,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}收入眼底的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.36,0:22:38.63,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}不可能尽然相同
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.85,0:22:50.26,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}无论心意 未来还是笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.47,0:22:57.17,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}对 还有素未谋面的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.94,0:23:10.69,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.58,0:23:28.68,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}虽然会有永恒和如烟以及孤单的夜晚
Comment: 0,0:23:21.93,0:23:25.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//------------------TEXT------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.85,0:02:22.86,TITLE,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(632,271.333)\fad(500,0)\blur1}守墓人诞生之地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.93,0:00:10.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「对我来说 世界就是极小的共同体
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.43,0:00:15.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打算经由破坏来拯救它」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.69,0:00:19.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾经这样对你说过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.89,0:00:20.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.85,0:00:25.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能帮我实现它吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.83,0:00:27.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.48,0:00:31.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果那样做能拯救世界的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.83,0:00:34.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.92,0:00:38.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之前 要找那个叫疤面的守墓人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.30,0:00:43.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系 我不急
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.15,0:02:29.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.46,0:02:34.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,318°
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.20,0:02:36.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西北方再向北3°
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.38,0:02:39.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次也分毫不差
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.05,0:02:45.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤力先生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.40,0:02:47.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽管笔直的向前开好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.62,0:02:49.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冲啊 冲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.80,0:02:51.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好嘞 出发咯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.31,0:02:55.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀呼 飞啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.97,0:03:02.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲爱的巫拉 还有齐利科
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.80,0:03:05.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接着昨天的信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.88,0:03:08.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是近况报告第4回
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.59,0:03:14.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样 成功从葛拉学院逃脱(？)的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.30,0:03:19.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将塔尼亚平安送回父母身边了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.26,0:03:28.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简言之 葛拉学园的大家也暂时安顿在了塔尼亚家的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.67,0:03:34.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过他们说总有一天会各自到自己该去的地方去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.58,0:03:42.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后 我们又飞驰在荒野上了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.77,0:03:47.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,踏上了寻找「在葛拉村时突然消失的疤面小姐」的旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.02,0:03:52.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而带路的是…赛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.19,0:04:00.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为赛莉卡曾在欧塔斯将疤面小姐呼唤到自己身边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.19,0:04:04.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以这次一定也能找到疤面小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.24,0:04:11.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 虽然现在有些迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.05,0:04:17.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追着疤面把她找到 真的是为她好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.40,0:04:20.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然之间说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.49,0:04:25.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 疤面怎么说都是个守墓人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.56,0:04:29.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,守墓人都是追寻着死者的气息独自旅行的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.48,0:04:35.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此 疤面现在不就回到了本来应有的样子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.28,0:04:39.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…也有道理
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.68,0:04:48.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…是否确实如此我想听疤面小姐亲口说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.88,0:04:51.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 我想见疤面小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.16,0:04:59.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要就这样诀别
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.65,0:05:01.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.75,0:05:07.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再怎么说 我那时应该多帮帮她的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.58,0:05:13.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在葛拉艾失踪之后 疤面变得非常不安定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.41,0:05:20.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚还紧紧抱着赛莉卡 下一刻就丢一边不管
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.35,0:05:26.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还以为她在发呆 突然又很害怕的样子开始发抖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.70,0:05:32.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道这很反常 但却什么都没帮到她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.25,0:05:33.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.00,0:06:01.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好好 还是西北方再向北3°
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.28,0:06:05.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找不到疤面小姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.52,0:06:08.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.21,0:06:11.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.13,0:07:01.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不早说今天你是生日呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.62,0:07:04.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…又没人问我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.12,0:07:07.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生日是一定要说出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.12,0:07:10.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是 要是蒂伊没想起来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.99,0:07:12.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就要出大事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.10,0:07:14.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是亚利斯的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.38,0:07:15.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.63,0:07:16.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.49,0:07:20.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生日是在…昨天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.18,0:07:21.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.36,0:07:23.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种小事无所谓啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.24,0:07:27.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔 要帮忙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.95,0:07:32.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢着 我的话还没讲完
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.52,0:07:34.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说讲完了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.66,0:07:37.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都说无所谓了 还有什么问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.10,0:07:40.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 这可是生日耶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.62,0:07:42.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要喊生日快乐耶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.51,0:07:45.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一年一度的重要活动耶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.85,0:07:46.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.60,0:07:50.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是现在哪还顾得上这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.87,0:07:54.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要拯救世界
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.39,0:08:00.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了达成目的 我什么都肯做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.50,0:08:03.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生日又算得了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.64,0:08:06.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你够…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.62,0:08:14.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以啊 亚利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.22,0:08:18.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不可以这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.66,0:08:24.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以 割舍掉这些
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.02,0:08:37.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生日 就应该要大家一起庆祝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.90,0:08:41.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚利斯 今年几岁了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.98,0:08:45.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十…六
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.73,0:08:52.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚利斯 十六岁生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.01,0:09:02.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起庆祝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.32,0:09:06.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤力先生 能做蛋糕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.00,0:09:07.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那当然
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.06,0:09:10.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.16,0:09:28.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.64,0:09:29.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 先等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.20,0:09:31.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来才是重头戏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.86,0:09:38.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦 快点吹灭它
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.39,0:09:41.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要好好许愿哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.07,0:09:54.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真香
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.90,0:10:04.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样 吓一跳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.62,0:10:09.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样呢 这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.23,0:10:11.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里可不行啊喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.18,0:10:12.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那这招怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.95,0:10:14.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更加不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.26,0:10:36.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔 没想到做父亲有模有样的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.71,0:10:44.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他…曾经是父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.93,0:10:50.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤力先生的妻子和女儿去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.71,0:10:54.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.55,0:10:59.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人或是守墓人都会变呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.24,0:11:03.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界还真是复杂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.06,0:11:08.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比我之前想像的还要更加 更加…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.69,0:11:12.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.46,0:11:14.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然你很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.12,0:11:18.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也曾到各处旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.12,0:11:22.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但从没见过像你这样的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.85,0:11:24.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.98,0:11:26.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正不是贬义啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.84,0:11:28.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 那根本不算回答…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.94,0:11:29.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.90,0:11:35.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 给我过生日
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.16,0:11:39.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.85,0:12:04.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻烦了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.59,0:12:07.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路越来越烂 再加上这能见度
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.66,0:12:11.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害的雾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.84,0:12:16.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厉害吗  反而让人觉得厌恶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.67,0:12:24.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她说别抱怨了 快走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.32,0:12:43.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 尤力先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.83,0:12:45.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么急刹车啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.37,0:13:06.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是…什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.96,0:13:09.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之先回车里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.70,0:13:12.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雾太大 要是走散了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.84,0:13:16.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤力先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.30,0:13:21.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,声音…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.64,0:13:24.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,声音消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.23,0:13:33.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们俩没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.18,0:13:40.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…刚才那是雷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.09,0:13:42.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.38,0:13:45.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,守墓人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.26,0:14:38.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.33,0:14:51.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多保重
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.32,0:14:53.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多保重
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.23,0:14:55.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多保重
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.10,0:15:10.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(670.4,644.8)}<story circle>
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.10,0:15:10.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是守墓人诞生之地吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.30,0:15:14.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是守墓人诞生的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.55,0:15:21.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们长得一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.15,0:15:25.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,守墓人就是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.82,0:15:31.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,数百人…多的时候是以数千人为单位被确认为同一个体
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.61,0:15:34.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如贝泽尔族
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.26,0:15:35.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蒂尼欧族之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.47,0:15:40.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,研究者们为同一类型的守墓人命名以区分
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.01,0:15:47.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 也有很多守墓人只被发现过一次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.63,0:15:49.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈娜就是那一类
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.22,0:15:59.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 居然来了这种鬼地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.50,0:16:08.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疤面小姐是想回到自己出生的地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.10,0:16:13.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.52,0:16:20.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是迄今为止最强烈的反应啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.81,0:16:23.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赛莉卡 难道疤面就在附近吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.04,0:16:24.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.17,0:16:30.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们真的打算去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.00,0:16:41.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这前方 守墓人诞生之地将会继续延伸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.44,0:16:47.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要回去咯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.09,0:16:50.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蒂伊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.54,0:16:52.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有不详的预感
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.80,0:16:56.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么这样…都一起到这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.81,0:16:57.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.05,0:17:09.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不知道我很反复无常吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.31,0:17:13.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蒂伊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.01,0:17:17.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这是什么表情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.88,0:17:20.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.25,0:17:31.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.21,0:17:35.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续前进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.88,0:17:44.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了 能见度越来越低了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.43,0:17:47.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得应该很近了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.35,0:17:50.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾 怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.84,0:17:52.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.24,0:17:59.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那还是慢慢前进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.74,0:18:21.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤力先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.95,0:18:24.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.28,0:18:26.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.57,0:18:36.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 尤力先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.45,0:18:42.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸…爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.31,0:18:47.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.37,0:18:51.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.99,0:18:54.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.99,0:19:10.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.05,0:19:13.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.27,0:19:20.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸将妈妈宝贵的梦想给…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.55,0:19:27.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 我真的什么都不明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.12,0:19:31.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.96,0:19:35.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这妈妈的梦想 是妈妈的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.08,0:19:38.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我记住
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.73,0:19:41.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你活下去唯一的话是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.72,0:19:42.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「想活下去」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.01,0:20:17.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疤面小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.28,0:20:21.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们来接你了 疤面小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.52,0:20:26.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没这个必要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.39,0:20:31.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是诞生于此的守墓人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.42,0:20:36.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唔…如果疤面小姐想作为曾经的守墓人一般活下去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.33,0:20:42.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我是…无法勉强你的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.28,0:20:43.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.14,0:20:46.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤力先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.51,0:20:51.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疤面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.32,0:20:53.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赛莉卡怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.82,0:20:57.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算就这样和赛莉卡分开吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.67,0:21:01.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.24,0:21:03.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要让她接近我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.47,0:21:06.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有她在 我就会…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.79,0:21:07.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疤面
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.59,0:21:10.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 我是守墓人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.70,0:21:14.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为守墓人要帮助所有的活人度过美好人生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.18,0:21:18.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.64,0:21:31.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疤面
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.33,0:21:33.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,守墓人是不会哭的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.67,0:21:43.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赛莉卡…赛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.83,0:21:47.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疤面
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.30,0:21:51.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从今往后 我会守护你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.44,0:21:53.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都别说 跟着我就好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.90,0:21:57.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.45,0:22:00.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔真有一手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.28,0:22:02.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这是表白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.87,0:22:03.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭…闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.38,0:22:06.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也会尽全力保护你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.00,0:22:08.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做好心理准备
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.18,0:22:12.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤力先生好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.65,0:22:13.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可靠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.90,0:22:13.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.93,0:22:33.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个镇叫什么名字
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.17,0:22:38.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欧斯提亚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.05,0:22:48.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们…三年四班被困在那个镇里了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.07,0:23:33.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎来到我们的故乡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.16,0:23:34.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾 软绵绵的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.85,0:23:35.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蒂伊还不是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.80,0:23:37.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日历是十四年前的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.00,0:23:38.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有死者的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.77,0:23:39.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里有我的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.28,0:23:43.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的梦想是拯救世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.84,0:23:43.80,TITLE,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(500,0)\blur1}三年四班 Ⅰ
